{"tid":361380,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"點解女人成日覺得自己成熟過男人？","createTime":"2017-08-16T05:47:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-16T08:06:50.000Z","uid":81234,"like":42,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3baf38b15e3c9022e09d550117b9763bf5ab7169","tid":361380,"uid":81234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T05:47:25.000Z","msg":"識勁多廿歲到三十幾歲既八婆<br />\n話咩覺得所有男仔都好唔成熟 話咩女人成熟過男人幾年<br />\n工作上定感情上都要踩住男人先覺得自己叻<br />\n<br />\n日日以為自己係成功既女強人 <br />\n其實根本九成男人會理你成唔成功 <br />\n只會理你靚唔靚 性格好唔好<br />\n唔通因為你事業有成就鍾意你咩 除非你好似小甜甜咁有錢啦 就算係都唔會真心<br />\n<br />\n八婆們<br />\n你果d叫勢利 叫現實 叫貪錢 叫輸打贏要<br />\n成熟？邊到成熟<br />\n釣金龜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 收兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 扮可憐踩住男同事上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 講是非排尻人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 曬名牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 去旅行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 去shopping<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n日日去蒲 玩夠要人埋單 <br />\n原來咁叫成熟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23bf731b88873b69a0e7dd1b5e74d5e24e88572f","tid":361380,"uid":91982,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T05:49:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fda81c18ceec3e04eae5d6ae34a1dd8c502f2a9e","tid":361380,"uid":82717,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T05:57:23.000Z","msg":"唔識或唔貪玩嘅人係覺得自己特別成熟"},{"pid":"8f5514ed7eb1fadc032e3d2ff6e2a283a64c3c58","tid":361380,"uid":81234,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T05:58:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔識或唔貪玩嘅人係覺得自己特別成熟</blockquote><br />\n岩 臭西同毒撚永遠覺得自己最成熟 連登大把"},{"pid":"fd30a1d45650fca7c23c97c0d1599242494deade","tid":361380,"uid":56432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T06:01:49.000Z","msg":"個人現實啲自私啲功利啲